<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding: 0;
    outline: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    max-width:700px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility !important;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased !important;
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

header {
    margin-top:20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    justify-content: center;
    line-height: 30px;
    border-bottom:  1px solid #ee4d64;
}

header span {
    font-size:13px;
    font-style: italic;
    color:#555;
}

header img{
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.data {
    margin-top:30px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 5px 10px;
}

.title {
    font-size:17px;
    margin-bottom:4px ;
}

.data ul li {
    list-style: none;
    line-height: 30px;
    margin-left: 20px;
    font-size:16px;
}

.data ul li .destaque{
    padding: 3px;
    background-color: #ee4d6541;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size:12px;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.info {
    margin-top:20px;
    line-height: 18px;
    font-size: 15px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
}

.info p {
    border:1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 5px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    width:48%;

}

.info .destaque {
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom:1px solid #ee4d6470;
}

footer {
    margin-top:50px;
    display:flex ;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size:13px;
    font-weight: bold;
}
</style>

<header>
  <img src="https://github.com/Rocketseat/bootcamp-gostack-desafio-03/blob/master/.github/logo.png?raw=true"/>
  <h1>{{name}}, Welcome to Gympoint</h1>
  <span>It is an indescribable pleasure to have you as a member of Gympoint.</span>
</header>

<div class="data">
  <p class="title">Some details of your registration:</p>
  <ul>
      <li>Your plan is the <span class="destaque">{{title}}</span>, duration in months: <span class="destaque">{{duration}}</span></li>
      <li>The total amount of this plan is R$ <span class="destaque">{{price}}</span></li>
      <li>You start at the gym in <span class="destaque">{{firstDay}}</span></li>
      <li>The plan ends in <span class="destaque">{{lastDay}}</span></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="data">
  <p class="title">With your registration <strong>{{id}}</strong>:</p>
  <ul>
      <li>You will check in daily.</li>
      <li>You can ask questions to the gym.</li>
      <li>You can consult the answers, which will also be sent by email.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
<div class="info">
  <p>Our gym works from <span class="destaque">Monday to Friday</span>, of <span class="destaque">5:00 AM to 11:00 PM</span>.</p>
  <p>We have instructors available throughout the gym.</p>
</div>
